{"word":"G498 - ἀντιτάσσομαι - antitássomai - an-tee-tas'-som-ahee - Oppose themselves","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντιτάσσομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antitássomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-tee-tas'-som-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Oppose themselves</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எதிர்த்துநில்"},{"paragraph":"to range in battle against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and the middle of <a href=\"#/G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so/5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>range oneself against</i>, that is, <i>oppose:</i> - oppose themselves, resist.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}